    "asOf": "2022-09-28",
    "date": "2022-11-21T23:05:20Z",
    "text": "Tribal Connect Act of 2022\n\nThis bill expands tribal access to the Schools and Libraries Universal Service Support (E-rate) program, which provides discounted broadband internet access and telecommunications services to certain schools and libraries. It also establishes a pilot program to provide broadband internet access service to essential community-serving institutions (e.g., community centers) located on tribal land."
